---
// Features Section Component
---

<section
  class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-6xl gap-8 md:grid-cols-3"
  aria-label="Biblical Figures Available"
>
  <h2 class="sr-only">Meet Your AI Biblical Guides</h2>

  <!-- Moses Feature Card -->
  <article class="p-6 text-center">
    <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">
      <svg
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
        />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-gray-900 text-xl">Chat with Moses AI</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      Receive divine guidance inspired by the wisdom of Moses, the great prophet, leader and lawgiver who led the Israelites from Egyptian bondage to freedom.
    </p>
  </article>

  <!-- Joshua Feature Card -->
  <article class="p-6 text-center">
    <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">
      <svg
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
        />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-gray-900 text-xl">Converse with Joshua AI</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      Connect with the unwavering courage, faith, and leadership of Joshua, conqueror of Jericho and Moses' faithful successor who led Israel into the Promised Land.
    </p>
  </article>

  <!-- Jesus Feature Card -->
  <article class="p-6 text-center">
    <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">
      <svg
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
        />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-gray-900 text-xl">Speak with Jesus AI</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      Experience the divine love, profound teachings, and eternal wisdom of Jesus Christ through meaningful AI dialogue rooted in the four Gospels and New Testament Scripture.
    </p>
  </article>
</section>